      <title>PZ Cussons 因尼日利亚奈拉贬值而下调前景和股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/pz-cussons-cuts-outlook-dividend-on-nigerian-naira-devaluation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PZ Cussons Plc 下调了利润预期，因为其尼日利亚业务继续受到奈拉贬值的影响，奈拉去年经历了历史上最大的跌幅。]]></description>
